snippet.title: Path of Exile Mobile Official Announcement
snippet.description:
Path of Exile's Mobile project was announced at ExileCon 2019 in Auckland, New Zealand. 

Find out more about Path of Exile Mobile here: https://www.pathofexile.com/mobile
